cli_resume_builder/
├── main.py                        # CLI entry point using Typer
│
├── commands/                      # Typer command modules
│   ├── init.py                    # `generate outline resume for experience`
│   ├── experience.py              # `resume experience add <repo> [--ai]`
│   ├── skills.py                  # (optional) manual skill edits
│   └── render.py                  # `Render to markdown/html || pdf`
│
├── utils/                         # Utility functions & API clients
│   ├── github_api.py              # Fetch repo metadata && languages for skills
│   ├── resume_io.py               # Load/save resume.yaml
│   └── claude_client.py           # Claude API integration for summaries
│
├── templates/                     # Resume rendering templates
│   └── resume.md.j2               # Jinja2 markdown template
│
├── resume.yaml || resume.json     # Auto-generated user résumé data
│
├── requirements.txt               # Python deps: typer, requests, PyYAML, jinja2, anthropic, weasyprint
├── .env                           # Holds ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (if dotenv support added)
└── README.md                      # For instruction && potentially hackathon presentation